summary:
Agile Product Owner with an MBA in Finance and Computer Science background. Experience in gathering and analyzing business/user requirements, leading websites and applications development, optimizing systems, improving and automating processes. Effective communicator who connects business and technical teams, takes ownership and inspires others for continuous improvement. Persistent, flexible and adaptable to change with great problem-solving capabilities and an eye for detail.

- The International Baccalaureate – business processes analysis and improvement; financial reporting; redesigned and updated external communication through the systems; event and project coordination, planning, logistics, contracting support for Regional Events and Conferences across EMEA

- British American Tobacco – Competitor intelligence, regional performance analysis and forecasting, macroeconomic analysis for the Western European Region

- MBA in Finance – Courses in Advanced Corporate Finance, Financial Risk Management, Quantitative Platform for Business, Strategy, Marketing, Operations Management

- Heineken – Project and event coordination; interface between suppliers and the company; marketing research and business intelligence

- Excellent written and verbal English, upper intermediate Dutch, native Russian, intermediate Spanish and Polish
